{
  "texts": [
    "Clinical features were the clinical assessment information, such as the Fugl-Meyer assessment score and the total months the patients had a stroke.",
    "Demographic features were age and sex.",
    "Various combinations of the above features were examined to build predictive machine-learning models for the percentage difference in the Wolf motor function test in different periods of the VRehab program.",
    "Combining all the features in the above four categories was found to significantly improve the performance of the predictive models.",
    "The machine-learning models were multiple linear regression and random forest, with the latter resulting in lower root mean square error."
  ]
}